      "name": "Mementotlan Akihiron",
      "effect": "If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can activate this effect; Level 9 or higher \"Memento\" monsters can attack directly this turn. If this card is destroyed by card effect: You can target 1 other \"Memento\" card in your GY or banishment; add it to your hand. If a \"Memento\" monster(s) in your hand and/or face-up field is destroyed by battle or card effect, while this card is in your GY: You can Special Summon this card. You can only use each effect of \"Mementotlan Akihiron\" once per turn.",
